Task 4: Virus & threat protection

This section is divided into Current threats and Settings.
Current Threats allows you to perform scans:

Quick scan: Checks common threat locations.
Full scan: Checks all files (can take over an hour).
Custom scan: User-selected locations.
Settings allow you to manage:

Real-time protection: Actively stops malware from running.
Cloud-delivered protection: Accesses the latest threat data from the cloud.
Exclusions: Items you tell the antivirus to ignore.

